article.description: — Darin Green Jr. posted 18 points, making four 3-pointers, as Central Florida routed Bethune-Cookman 81-45 on Sunday.
article.headline: Green Jr. scores 18 to carry UCF over Bethune-Cookman 81-45
article.linkText: Green Jr. scores 18 to carry UCF over Bethune-Cookman 81-45
article.story: ORLANDO, Fla. -- — Darin Green Jr. posted 18 points, making four 3-pointers, as Central Florida routed Bethune-Cookman 81-45 on Sunday. Tyem Freeman had 12 points for Central Florida (5-2). Brandon Mahan added 11 points. C.J. Walker had 10 points. Joe French had 12 points for the Wildcats (1-7), whose losing streak stretched to four games. Marcus Garrett added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
